high_descs: Head towards to the microwave.
Take a butterknife from the microwave.
Head towards the potato table.
Cut the potato and keep the knife in the microwave.
Keep the knife in the microwave.
Head towards to the butterknife on the coffee table.
Head towards the diningtable.
Take a slice of potato from the table.
Keep the potato inside the microwave.
Heat the potato in the microwave.
Take the potato out and head towards to the fridge.
Keep the potato slice inside the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Take a slice of potato and keep it inside the fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and enter into another room. Then turn left to reach the microwave on the microwave oven table.
Open the oven and take a butterknife from the oven and close it.
Turn back and take a left turn to reach the potato on the round table.
Cut the potato into pieces which is kept on the round table.
Turn left and walk towards the microwave on the oven table.
Open the microwave and put the butterknife into the microwave and close it.
Turn back and take a left turn to reach the diningtable again.
Take a piece of potato from the round table.
Turn left and walk towards the microwave table again.
Open the oven and put the potato piece into the oven and close it. Then after a few seconds open the oven and take out the fried potato piece and close the oven.
Turn left and walk nearer to the fridge.
Put the potato piece in the fridge and close the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Put the Potato piece in the Fridge

high_descs: Turn right go straight turn left to the microwave.
Take the butterknife from the oven
Turn around then turn left to the potato table.
Cut the potato on the diningtable.
Turn left to the microwave.
Put the butterknife in the microwave.
Turn around then turn left to the diningtable.
Take the potato.
Turn left to the microwave.
Put the potato in the oven, heat it, and take it back.
Turn around then turn right to the fridge.
Place the potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Take the knife Cut the potato heat it and Place it in the fridge
